media:group.media:title: How Much Faster Does A SSL Shoot? (feat. SunlessKhan, FreaKii, Justuszzz)
media:group.media:description:
How much more power do the higher ranks get on shots, and what sets pros apart from the rest? A large dataset of 743 people will hopefully shed some light on these questions. For those wondering about the input lag experiment: https://experiment.rocketscience.fyi I'm writing my thesis on it which is way more thorough work than what I'm discussing here, so that will still take a while and I won't release preliminary results.
